Name: Aguila Ltd
Description:
Founded on August 14 1955 buses eagle was a company witness and tool for the growth of the population of Baja California. A group of visionaries who based on the capital of the then territory of southern Baja California (La Paz) saw the opportunity to communicate the communities that shape the unique expressions of hospitality tranquility and magnificence taking as a framework the natural beauties and the contrasts of the landscape. We discovered that communicating was our business and serving our pride.With these ideals as a creed we are currently the bus company with the highest coverage and demand in the states that make up the peninsula of Baja California. Connecting through the transpeninsular highway the beauty of the cabos beaches with its excellent hotel infrastructure with the cosmopolitan business life of the border cities of Tijuana and Mexicali. As well as the historic towns that throughout our journeys paint the unique and magical altarpieces for those who seek to know and explore.,123456789,Stavri,Goshev,Tvardica str.10,0889199891
